WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:05.759
Hey, good morning family. I have a

00:00:03.360 --> 00:00:07.279
great video here for you. I have a

00:00:05.759 --> 00:00:09.360
great testimony—something that I've

00:00:07.279 --> 00:00:11.840
been believing God for, and the Lord came

00:00:09.360 --> 00:00:14.160
through. I just came on today

00:00:11.840 --> 00:00:17.439
to tell you about the goodness of God

00:00:14.160 --> 00:00:19.840
and what faith can do. First

00:00:17.440 --> 00:00:22.240
of all, I want to say thank you for all

00:00:19.840 --> 00:00:24.240
the likes, all the shares, and all

00:00:22.240 --> 00:00:27.439
the kind words in the comment

00:00:24.240 --> 00:00:29.119
section. God is so good. He told me to

00:00:27.439 --> 00:00:31.679
start this channel back at the first of

00:00:29.119 --> 00:00:34.079
the year, and to see what the Lord has

00:00:31.679 --> 00:00:36.399
done in such a short amount of time has

00:00:34.079 --> 00:00:37.920
been amazing. I just want to

00:00:36.399 --> 00:00:39.920
say thank you from

00:00:37.920 --> 00:00:41.680
the bottom of my heart, for my wife's

00:00:39.920 --> 00:00:43.280
heart, and for my children. We just want to

00:00:41.680 --> 00:00:44.879
say thank you for all the love gifts and

00:00:43.280 --> 00:00:46.800
for all of the support that you're

00:00:44.879 --> 00:00:48.480
showing us. We just want to let you

00:00:46.800 --> 00:00:50.959
know we pray for you. We're believing

00:00:48.480 --> 00:00:52.480
for your miracles, for a

00:00:50.960 --> 00:00:54.399
turnaround in your finances, and

00:00:52.480 --> 00:00:57.360
for healing in your

00:00:54.399 --> 00:01:00.559
bodies. I just believe that

00:00:57.360 --> 00:01:03.600
nothing is impossible to him who believes,

00:01:00.559 --> 00:01:05.679
and God is still doing miracles today.

00:01:03.600 --> 00:01:08.159
Here's a miracle that God did for

00:01:05.680 --> 00:01:10.560
me. At the beginning of this year, I

00:01:08.159 --> 00:01:13.280
had the same mower. I have a little

00:01:10.560 --> 00:01:15.920
over an acre of land that I take care

00:01:13.280 --> 00:01:17.200
of every week in the

00:01:15.920 --> 00:01:18.400
summer and the spring, and

00:01:17.200 --> 00:01:20.159
then through the fall. I have a lot

00:01:18.400 --> 00:01:22.159
of trees, and the trees drop all the

00:01:20.159 --> 00:01:25.200
leaves. I've had the same

00:01:22.159 --> 00:01:28.479
mower now for going on 20 years.

00:01:28.479 --> 00:01:34.158
The transmission belt that makes it go

00:01:31.600 --> 00:01:35.439
was slipping really bad.

00:01:34.159 --> 00:01:37.520
I started looking at how much

00:01:35.439 --> 00:01:39.839
mowers cost and pricing them.

00:01:37.520 --> 00:01:41.920
For my land and how much of a mower I

00:01:39.840 --> 00:01:44.400
needed, it was going to cost thousands

00:01:41.920 --> 00:01:46.159
and thousands of dollars. I said,

00:01:44.400 --> 00:01:47.520
'Lord, I don't

00:01:46.159 --> 00:01:49.520
want to spend that kind of money on a

00:01:47.520 --> 00:01:52.079
credit card or try to do this right now.

00:01:49.520 --> 00:01:54.000
I'm just going to use this mower as

00:01:52.079 --> 00:01:56.079
much as I can.'I

00:01:54.000 --> 00:01:58.640
anointed it with oil, started praying

00:01:56.079 --> 00:02:00.880
over my mower, and I just had to drive really

00:01:58.640 --> 00:02:03.119
slow.

00:02:00.880 --> 00:02:05.119
Here we are in

00:02:03.119 --> 00:02:06.719
August, and all through the

00:02:05.119 --> 00:02:08.800
summer, it was

00:02:06.719 --> 00:02:10.478
just driving really slow; it took

00:02:08.800 --> 00:02:13.680
me forever to mow this

00:02:10.479 --> 00:02:15.520
land. I didn't

00:02:13.680 --> 00:02:16.959
complain; it was

00:02:15.520 --> 00:02:18.319
irritating, but I just used

00:02:16.959 --> 00:02:20.560
it as prayer time. The

00:02:18.319 --> 00:02:22.720
more time I had to mow, the more time I spent

00:02:20.560 --> 00:02:24.879
praying in the spirit and

00:02:22.720 --> 00:02:26.560
seeking Him. It was

00:02:24.879 --> 00:02:29.359
just my private time

00:02:26.560 --> 00:02:31.040
mowing grass. Lo and behold, I was

00:02:29.360 --> 00:02:33.440
outside and I was weed-eating around

00:02:31.040 --> 00:02:37.040
my yard tonight when a lady from the

00:02:33.440 --> 00:02:40.879
church drove up in a truck with

00:02:37.040 --> 00:02:43.519
a mower on a trailer in the back.

00:02:40.879 --> 00:02:46.720
She jumped out of

00:02:43.519 --> 00:02:49.840
the truck and said, 'Brandon,

00:02:46.720 --> 00:02:52.640
the Lord spoke to me in my yard last

00:02:49.840 --> 00:02:55.440
night

00:02:52.640 --> 00:02:57.760
and told me to come and

00:02:55.440 --> 00:03:00.640
bless you with this mower. I bought it

00:02:57.760 --> 00:03:02.720
last year and I paid $7,000 for it.'She

00:03:00.640 --> 00:03:04.879
said it's brand new and has

00:03:02.720 --> 00:03:06.800
the bagger and everything. This

00:03:04.879 --> 00:03:08.959
mower is top of the line—the Cadillac of mowers. It's

00:03:06.800 --> 00:03:10.879
one of the best

00:03:08.959 --> 00:03:12.480
mowers you can buy on the market;

00:03:10.879 --> 00:03:15.120
it doesn't get any better, really.

00:03:12.480 --> 00:03:17.119
The engine

00:03:15.120 --> 00:03:20.000
is really big. This

00:03:17.120 --> 00:03:22.800
sucker's huge. She

00:03:20.000 --> 00:03:25.760
and her husband got out and said, 'We

00:03:22.800 --> 00:03:28.400
believe the Lord spoke to us

00:03:25.760 --> 00:03:29.920
to give you this mower to use for your

00:03:28.400 --> 00:03:32.400
land.'I

00:03:29.920 --> 00:03:34.238
said, 'Are you kidding me?'and they

00:03:32.400 --> 00:03:36.239
said, 'Yeah.'She was crying and

00:03:34.239 --> 00:03:37.840
he was crying;

00:03:36.239 --> 00:03:40.000
it was a

00:03:37.840 --> 00:03:42.480
sacrificial gift.

00:03:40.000 --> 00:03:44.560
I was so taken aback by it. I just said,

00:03:42.480 --> 00:03:47.280
'Praise God,'because I've been

00:03:44.560 --> 00:03:49.840
believing for this mower and the Lord

00:03:47.280 --> 00:03:51.599
came through. I'm

00:03:49.840 --> 00:03:53.360
not bragging about what God did; I'm rejoicing

00:03:51.599 --> 00:03:55.839
in it.

00:03:53.360 --> 00:03:58.560
I'm trying to tell you that faith can do

00:03:55.840 --> 00:04:00.319
anything. If you want to believe for anything—it

00:03:58.560 --> 00:04:02.959
doesn't matter how big or

00:04:00.319 --> 00:04:05.200
how small—God is able to

00:04:02.959 --> 00:04:07.760
provide. He came

00:04:05.200 --> 00:04:09.839
through for me again.

00:04:07.760 --> 00:04:12.640
They rolled that mower down

00:04:09.840 --> 00:04:14.480
off that trailer and said,

00:04:12.640 --> 00:04:16.079
'Here you go.'They taught me how to use it—it

00:04:14.480 --> 00:04:18.560
took a bit because

00:04:16.079 --> 00:04:20.639
it had all these buttons and features.

00:04:18.560 --> 00:04:22.479
It was just amazing.

00:04:20.639 --> 00:04:25.040
As

00:04:22.479 --> 00:04:27.440
I

00:04:25.040 --> 00:04:29.600
said, it has the bagger for

00:04:27.440 --> 00:04:31.520
the leaves for the coming fall.

00:04:29.600 --> 00:04:34.320
Everything I ever wanted

00:04:31.520 --> 00:04:36.159
in a mower, God gave it to me today. I

00:04:34.320 --> 00:04:39.040
just want to tell you right now how good

00:04:36.160 --> 00:04:41.440
God is. God is a good God, He loves

00:04:39.040 --> 00:04:44.400
you so much, and He provided for me again

00:04:41.440 --> 00:04:46.320
today with something that was

00:04:44.400 --> 00:04:48.880
like the Cadillac of mowers. It's

00:04:46.320 --> 00:04:50.479
not like a little push

00:04:48.880 --> 00:04:53.440
mower; He gave me the best

00:04:50.479 --> 00:04:54.800
of the best of a rider and, in

00:04:53.440 --> 00:04:56.479
the world scene, I'm just telling you

00:04:54.800 --> 00:04:58.160
it doesn't get any better than that.

00:05:00.560 --> 00:05:05.600
If God can do it for me, He can do it

00:05:02.639 --> 00:05:08.080
for you. I didn't complain about it; I

00:05:05.600 --> 00:05:10.000
tried to be thankful for what I had and keep

00:05:08.080 --> 00:05:11.359
a good attitude, regardless

00:05:10.000 --> 00:05:13.120
if that belt was slipping. I

00:05:11.360 --> 00:05:15.680
anointed it with oil and kept praying

00:05:13.120 --> 00:05:17.440
over it, 'Little mower, you're

00:05:15.680 --> 00:05:19.199
going to last all through the summer;

00:05:17.440 --> 00:05:20.560
you're not going to fall apart.'It

00:05:19.199 --> 00:05:21.759
kept getting worse and worse, but I

00:05:20.560 --> 00:05:23.120
kept praying

00:05:21.759 --> 00:05:24.880
in the spirit and

00:05:23.120 --> 00:05:26.560
laying hands on my mower: 'Mower, you're

00:05:24.880 --> 00:05:28.560
going to work today when I need you to

00:05:26.560 --> 00:05:30.080
work.'I

00:05:28.560 --> 00:05:32.160
told my wife,

00:05:30.080 --> 00:05:33.520
'It's okay. It's prayer time. We'll just

00:05:32.160 --> 00:05:35.039
keep a good attitude and just keep going.'I

00:05:33.520 --> 00:05:36.639
said at the end when

00:05:35.039 --> 00:05:37.599
they have a big sale sometime, we're

00:05:36.639 --> 00:05:40.400
going to find one. So I looked at

00:05:37.600 --> 00:05:41.840
Craigslist and Facebook

00:05:40.400 --> 00:05:43.280
Marketplace. I was always looking, saying,

00:05:41.840 --> 00:05:45.198
'Father, I thank You that You're

00:05:43.280 --> 00:05:46.880
going to provide something good and I'm

00:05:45.199 --> 00:05:48.400
going to get it for a good deal.'I

00:05:46.880 --> 00:05:49.919
kept thanking

00:05:48.400 --> 00:05:51.599
Him all the time, 'Thank You, Lord, that

00:05:49.919 --> 00:05:54.159
You've got this. I thank You, Father,

00:05:51.600 --> 00:05:55.520
that You supply for my

00:05:55.520 --> 00:05:58.400
needs.'I

00:05:58.400 --> 00:06:01.520
kept saying to myself,

00:05:59.919 --> 00:06:04.318
'I'm not going to complain.'I thank You, Lord, that

00:06:01.520 --> 00:06:06.000
all my needs are met

00:06:04.319 --> 00:06:08.080
according to Your riches and glory, and

00:06:06.000 --> 00:06:09.840
this mower is even a concern to You.

00:06:08.080 --> 00:06:12.318
I kept

00:06:09.840 --> 00:06:14.560
mowing week after

00:06:12.319 --> 00:06:16.560
week, and

00:06:14.560 --> 00:06:19.440
all of a sudden, a breakthrough comes.

00:06:16.560 --> 00:06:22.880
That's the way God moves.

00:06:19.440 --> 00:06:25.680
Breakthrough comes. Faith

00:06:22.880 --> 00:06:29.120
calls those things that be not as though

00:06:25.680 --> 00:06:31.520
they were. The same faith that will

00:06:29.120 --> 00:06:34.000
move a mountain will produce a mower,

00:06:31.520 --> 00:06:35.758
a healing, or

00:06:34.000 --> 00:06:38.080
whatever you need—an

00:06:35.759 --> 00:06:40.800
electric bill paid or

00:06:38.080 --> 00:06:44.960
some food for your children.

00:06:40.800 --> 00:06:47.520
God is a provider.

00:06:47.520 --> 00:06:51.039
I'm encouraged because

00:06:49.360 --> 00:06:52.560
it was a great breakthrough.

00:06:51.039 --> 00:06:54.080
When that mower

00:06:52.560 --> 00:06:56.160
turned that corner tonight when I was

00:06:54.080 --> 00:06:59.039
out there weed-eating in my yard, I

00:06:56.160 --> 00:07:00.960
thought, 'What in the world?'I noticed the truck and thought they were

00:06:59.039 --> 00:07:03.599
coming

00:07:00.960 --> 00:07:04.960
to

00:07:04.960 --> 00:07:08.159
help

00:07:05.919 --> 00:07:10.639
me mow; I had no idea that they were

00:07:08.160 --> 00:07:12.880
going to bless me with this high-dollar

00:07:10.639 --> 00:07:14.319
mower.

00:07:12.880 --> 00:07:16.319
I just wanted to give God

00:07:14.319 --> 00:07:21.120
the praise for it. The Lord has been

00:07:16.319 --> 00:07:23.919
speaking to me about 2024.

00:07:21.120 --> 00:07:26.479
I want you all to be encouraged;

00:07:23.919 --> 00:07:28.719
there is a major financial shifting

00:07:26.479 --> 00:07:31.440
about to take place.

00:07:28.720 --> 00:07:34.880
You need to

00:07:31.440 --> 00:07:36.960
get the Word down inside of you.

00:07:36.960 --> 00:07:41.840
I was driving down the road

00:07:39.280 --> 00:07:43.919
praying in the spirit and the Lord warned

00:07:41.840 --> 00:07:47.119
me, 'Brandon, there are

00:07:43.919 --> 00:07:50.560
very sobering days coming to America and

00:07:47.120 --> 00:07:51.919
around the world.'Very sobering days.

00:07:50.560 --> 00:07:53.919
And I thought, "Well, that doesn't sound

00:07:51.919 --> 00:07:56.479
like a real good word."He said, "But

00:07:53.919 --> 00:07:58.318
Brandon, what is the opposite of

00:07:56.479 --> 00:08:02.000
