00:07:58.319 --> 00:08:04.240
said, "Being drunk. You

00:08:02.000 --> 00:08:06.960
need to be filled with the

00:08:04.240 --> 00:08:09.280
Holy Ghost. You need to stay full with

00:08:06.960 --> 00:08:11.758
the Holy Ghost at all times to get

00:08:09.280 --> 00:08:14.638
through the days ahead. You need to get

00:08:11.759 --> 00:08:17.599
laughter down on the inside of you and

00:08:14.639 --> 00:08:19.520
get that Holy Ghost

00:08:17.599 --> 00:08:21.360
bubbling

00:08:19.520 --> 00:08:23.840
up on the inside of you

00:08:21.360 --> 00:08:26.560
to make it for what's coming."He

00:08:23.840 --> 00:08:28.719
told me, he said, "Do you remember, son?"And

00:08:26.560 --> 00:08:30.720
this is just the way we talk.

00:08:30.720 --> 00:08:34.640
"Do you remember

00:08:32.479 --> 00:08:37.200
about Mary Poppins whenever they were

00:08:34.640 --> 00:08:39.360
drinking the stuff? I love

00:08:37.200 --> 00:08:41.279
to laugh."He said, "That's the way you

00:08:39.360 --> 00:08:43.599
need to be. I love to laugh. You need to

00:08:41.279 --> 00:08:45.839
be filled with the Holy Ghost

00:08:43.599 --> 00:08:47.760
and laughter."And I've told you all

00:08:45.839 --> 00:08:50.640
this before, but the Lord reminded me

00:08:47.760 --> 00:08:54.080
again to tell you: you need to be filled

00:08:50.640 --> 00:08:56.319
with a refreshing,

00:08:54.080 --> 00:08:59.600
drinking

00:08:56.320 --> 00:09:01.360
of the spirit through praise.

00:08:59.600 --> 00:09:04.080
You need to get into the spirit of

00:09:01.360 --> 00:09:06.800
praise in your house, worshiping Him and

00:09:04.080 --> 00:09:09.839
thanksgiving and praise

00:09:06.800 --> 00:09:12.399
and adoration. "God, thank you for

00:09:09.839 --> 00:09:14.800
all that you've done for my home,"and

00:09:12.399 --> 00:09:17.200
get in that vein because

00:09:17.200 --> 00:09:22.320
when praises go up,

00:09:20.160 --> 00:09:23.920
blessings come down. I'm telling you, I

00:09:22.320 --> 00:09:25.040
was in a state of prayer last

00:09:23.920 --> 00:09:26.800
night. I was trying to tell you, and I

00:09:25.040 --> 00:09:29.599
kind of skipped around here

00:09:26.800 --> 00:09:31.599
about 2024 and what He was warning

00:09:29.600 --> 00:09:34.080
me about, and it's going to be a

00:09:31.600 --> 00:09:37.360
year that we soar. It's time for the

00:09:34.080 --> 00:09:40.160
body of Christ to start taking the

00:09:37.360 --> 00:09:43.600
dominion and our authority over the land

00:09:40.160 --> 00:09:47.120
and walking in a presence on our lives.

00:09:43.600 --> 00:09:49.040
We will soar in '24. Remember that it's a

00:09:47.120 --> 00:09:51.360
good year. It's not going to be a bad

00:09:49.040 --> 00:09:53.839
year. And what the devil meant for bad,

