00:11:52.560 --> 00:11:58.800
into good ground. You need to

00:11:54.800 --> 00:12:01.920
believe God because the harvest comes by sowing

00:11:58.800 --> 00:12:04.160
seed. If you're not sowing seed,

00:12:01.920 --> 00:12:07.920
you can't believe God for a harvest.

00:12:04.160 --> 00:12:11.120
I tithe. I give

00:12:07.920 --> 00:12:13.199
regularly as much as I can. And I sow

00:12:11.120 --> 00:12:16.160
those seeds and I believe and He

00:12:13.200 --> 00:12:18.959
provides. But if you're not sowing seed,

00:12:16.160 --> 00:12:21.839
don't expect a harvest in that area.

00:12:18.959 --> 00:12:24.560
What you sow, you'll reap. Whatsoever a

00:12:21.839 --> 00:12:27.279
man soweth, that shall he also reap.

00:12:24.560 --> 00:12:29.839
It's a law. If you sow corn into the ground,

00:12:27.279 --> 00:12:32.560
you're going to reap back corn. If

00:12:29.839 --> 00:12:34.160
you sow peas into the ground, you're

00:12:32.560 --> 00:12:37.680
going to reap back peas. If you sow

00:12:34.160 --> 00:12:39.760
potatoes and so on, the same thing. You sow

00:12:37.680 --> 00:12:42.079
into the kingdom of God and you

00:12:39.760 --> 00:12:44.240
bless ministries. You help people out

00:12:42.079 --> 00:12:46.719
and God's going to bless you: good

00:12:44.240 --> 00:12:48.959
measure, pressed down, shaken together,

00:12:46.720 --> 00:12:51.040
and running over, shall men give unto

00:12:48.959 --> 00:12:53.599
your bosom. He'll give you creative

00:12:51.040 --> 00:12:55.439
ideas to get wealth. He'll bless you so

00:12:53.600 --> 00:12:57.120
that you can be a blessing to others.

00:12:55.440 --> 00:12:59.200
It's not always about hoarding

00:12:57.120 --> 00:13:00.959
things on yourself. It's about being a

00:12:59.200 --> 00:13:02.880
blessing to the person in the

00:13:00.959 --> 00:13:05.040
line at the grocery store. They may not

00:13:02.880 --> 00:13:07.040
have grocery money to buy any

00:13:05.040 --> 00:13:09.199
groceries. They may be running

00:13:07.040 --> 00:13:10.880
low, but you go in there and you show

00:13:09.200 --> 00:13:12.639
the love of God, and the Holy

00:13:10.880 --> 00:13:14.480
Ghost speaks to you and he tells

00:13:12.639 --> 00:13:16.160
you, "Hey, you see that person right

00:13:14.480 --> 00:13:17.440
there? They don't have the money to buy

00:13:16.160 --> 00:13:19.279
their groceries. They're running

00:13:17.440 --> 00:13:21.200
real low on finances, but you can tell

00:13:19.279 --> 00:13:23.200
them Jesus loves them and buy their

00:13:21.200 --> 00:13:25.839
groceries today."But you can't do that

00:13:23.200 --> 00:13:28.720
broke. You can't do that bound. You've got

00:13:25.839 --> 00:13:30.880
to be treading

00:13:28.720 --> 00:13:33.040
water, not sinking in the water. We've

00:13:30.880 --> 00:13:34.480
got to be above and not beneath. We've got

00:13:33.040 --> 00:13:37.439
to go through and not go

00:13:34.480 --> 00:13:40.079
under. God has the cattle

00:13:37.440 --> 00:13:42.240
on a thousand hills and He has given it

00:13:40.079 --> 00:13:44.399
to us. He said, "I've given you dominion

00:13:42.240 --> 00:13:47.360
and authority and power in this earth.

00:13:44.399 --> 00:13:49.920
Go and take dominion. Subdue

00:13:47.360 --> 00:13:52.000
it just like He told Adam."And

00:13:49.920 --> 00:13:54.319
we have that same power on the

00:13:52.000 --> 00:13:57.600
inside of us to subdue and

00:13:54.320 --> 00:13:59.440
take dominion and authority over things.

00:13:57.600 --> 00:14:01.040
And God wants us to be a blessing to our

00:13:59.440 --> 00:14:03.519
neighbor.

00:14:01.040 --> 00:14:05.599
What's coming is going to be bad

00:14:03.519 --> 00:14:07.760
in the natural. I hope you all

00:14:05.600 --> 00:14:11.199
understand me. I do not try to preach

00:14:07.760 --> 00:14:14.240
fear, but I need to warn you again.

00:14:11.199 --> 00:14:17.680
Listen to me. A great shaking is

00:14:14.240 --> 00:14:20.240
coming. It is a massive shaking. It

00:14:17.680 --> 00:14:22.319
will be very hard for some people.

00:14:20.240 --> 00:14:24.000
And if you are not able to be a blessing

00:14:22.320 --> 00:14:26.320
to your neighbors around you that don't

00:14:24.000 --> 00:14:28.240
know Jesus Christ, you're missing it.

00:14:26.320 --> 00:14:30.880
We've got to come up another level. I

00:14:28.240 --> 00:14:34.320
saw it again in the spirit. I saw a

00:14:30.880 --> 00:14:37.199
great financial harvest. They were

00:14:34.320 --> 00:14:39.600
like dominoes stacked up. And I saw the

00:14:37.199 --> 00:14:41.199
years and the months ahead. And the Lord

00:14:39.600 --> 00:14:42.639
painted it out in front of me and He

00:14:41.199 --> 00:14:44.959
told me, He said, "There's going to be a

00:14:42.639 --> 00:14:47.360
financial shifting. There's going to be

00:14:44.959 --> 00:14:50.319
a catastrophic event. There's going to

00:14:47.360 --> 00:14:51.920
be an outpouring of my spirit.

00:14:50.320 --> 00:14:54.560
There's going to be a great

00:14:51.920 --> 00:14:56.319
harvest of souls."But He told me, He

00:14:54.560 --> 00:15:00.479
said, "Brandon, that's what I'm trying to

00:14:56.320 --> 00:15:02.720
tell you again. 2024 you will soar. It's

00:15:00.480 --> 00:15:05.760
time to come up another level. It's time

00:15:02.720 --> 00:15:07.839
to do things greater. I will provide all

00:15:05.760 --> 00:15:12.319
your needs according to My riches in glory."And

00:15:07.839 --> 00:15:14.880
I saw into 2024, and 2024 is

00:15:12.320 --> 00:15:16.560
not a bad year. It's a blessed year. I'm

00:15:14.880 --> 00:15:18.399
telling you. But like I said, it's like

00:15:16.560 --> 00:15:19.839
a

00:15:18.399 --> 00:15:22.160
coin.

00:15:19.839 --> 00:15:24.320
You can either

00:15:22.160 --> 00:15:27.360
focus on the bad

00:15:24.320 --> 00:15:30.880
or you can focus on the good. It's that

00:15:27.360 --> 00:15:33.839
thin. But it's a choice. You can praise

00:15:30.880 --> 00:15:36.800
Him through the storm and speak to your

00:15:33.839 --> 00:15:39.519
storm and tell it to be still, or you

00:15:36.800 --> 00:15:43.040
can let the storm overtake you. But you

00:15:39.519 --> 00:15:46.240
are in charge of your destiny. But you

00:15:43.040 --> 00:15:48.719
speaking out of your mouth, "Well, my

00:15:46.240 --> 00:15:51.040
life's never going to change. My life's

00:15:48.720 --> 00:15:53.600
never going to get better. All

00:15:51.040 --> 00:15:55.199
things are falling apart for me,"you're

00:15:53.600 --> 00:15:58.320
going to start living it. You can look

00:15:55.199 --> 00:16:00.319
around you and think, "Man, my life is

00:15:58.320 --> 00:16:02.800
looking terrible.

00:16:00.320 --> 00:16:05.279
My car is falling

00:16:02.800 --> 00:16:07.040
apart. My house has a leaky

00:16:05.279 --> 00:16:09.759
roof."But

00:16:07.040 --> 00:16:13.120
I'm telling you, a lot of what we

00:16:09.759 --> 00:16:16.240
live today is what we spoke 10 years

00:16:13.120 --> 00:16:18.079
ago, what we believed 5 years ago.

00:16:16.240 --> 00:16:20.560
Life and death are in the power of your

00:16:18.079 --> 00:16:23.199
tongue. And the Bible also says your

00:16:20.560 --> 00:16:25.920
tongue is the pen of a ready

00:16:23.199 --> 00:16:28.479
writer. And so you are writing your

00:16:25.920 --> 00:16:31.279
destiny, your future, out by what you

00:16:28.480 --> 00:16:33.519
speak. If you're saying things

00:16:31.279 --> 00:16:35.680
out of your mouth that are ugly

00:16:33.519 --> 00:16:37.519
and bad and you're cursing your wife—"Well,

00:16:35.680 --> 00:16:39.040
you're a no-good so-and-so"—guess

00:16:37.519 --> 00:16:41.199
what? You're going to start to reap a no-good so-and-so

00:16:39.040 --> 00:16:43.439
because you have

00:16:41.199 --> 00:16:45.199
authority over your house, husbands. You

00:16:43.440 --> 00:16:46.800
have authority over your children. You

00:16:45.199 --> 00:16:48.560
have authority over your wife. God gave

00:16:46.800 --> 00:16:50.479
you dominion over that home. And when

00:16:48.560 --> 00:16:52.638
you start speaking trash over your kids—"Well,

00:16:50.480 --> 00:16:54.240
Johnny,

00:16:52.639 --> 00:16:55.759
he's out there and he's just a no-good so-and-so.

00:16:54.240 --> 00:16:57.600
He's out doing drugs,

00:16:55.759 --> 00:17:00.399
sleeping around, doing all this stuff"—no,

00:16:57.600 --> 00:17:02.560
you've got to change

00:17:00.399 --> 00:17:04.799
your words. You've got to start speaking

00:17:02.560 --> 00:17:07.438
into that circumstance, saying, "No,

00:17:04.799 --> 00:17:09.359
Johnny's full of the Holy Ghost. He's

00:17:07.439 --> 00:17:11.199
full of the life and the power of God,

00:17:09.359 --> 00:17:13.359
and God's going to deliver him and use

00:17:11.199 --> 00:17:15.520
him for the kingdom. Things are going to

00:17:13.359 --> 00:17:17.760
get better in Johnny's life."I don't know

00:17:15.520 --> 00:17:20.319
what's going to happen to the

00:17:17.760 --> 00:17:24.079
person next door, but as for me and

00:17:20.319 --> 00:17:25.599
my house, we will serve the Lord. And

00:17:24.079 --> 00:17:28.000
that's the kind of words you've got to

00:17:25.599 --> 00:17:30.080
start saying. You've got to speak life into

00:17:28.000 --> 00:17:31.919
your circumstances. You've got to speak

00:17:30.080 --> 00:17:33.678
life into your children. You've got to

00:17:31.919 --> 00:17:35.760
speak life into your wife. And

00:17:33.679 --> 00:17:37.280
wives, you need to speak life into your

00:17:35.760 --> 00:17:39.440
husband. You don't need to be out

00:17:37.280 --> 00:17:41.760
cursing him: "Oh, he's just a drunk."No,

00:17:39.440 --> 00:17:43.919
he's not a drunk. He's full of the

00:17:41.760 --> 00:17:46.160
Holy Ghost. He's full of the wine of the

00:17:43.919 --> 00:17:48.720
Holy Ghost. He's going to be

00:17:46.160 --> 00:17:50.559
leading our family into victory. He's

00:17:48.720 --> 00:17:52.320
not going to be out doing bars and

00:17:50.559 --> 00:17:54.080
cheating and doing all that stuff. He's

00:17:52.320 --> 00:17:55.918
going to be in here preaching the word

00:17:54.080 --> 00:17:57.918
of God and leading this family into

00:17:55.919 --> 00:18:00.240
victory.

00:17:57.919 --> 00:18:02.880
You have to speak to your circumstances.

00:18:00.240 --> 00:18:04.480
Do you understand? Like I told you a

00:18:02.880 --> 00:18:06.480
thousand times, it feels like your

00:18:04.480 --> 00:18:08.880
mountain has to hear your voice. But

00:18:06.480 --> 00:18:11.120
what you live—I'll say it again—what

00:18:08.880 --> 00:18:13.280
you're living right now, what you're

00:18:11.120 --> 00:18:15.600
having in your life right now is a

00:18:13.280 --> 00:18:19.520
result of what you said yesterday.

00:18:15.600 --> 00:18:22.559
Remember that you have got to speak life

00:18:19.520 --> 00:18:25.039
into your circumstances. You have to

00:18:22.559 --> 00:18:27.360
because life and death is in

00:18:25.039 --> 00:18:28.799
the power of the tongue. It's so

00:18:27.360 --> 00:18:31.039
important that you hear what I'm telling

00:18:28.799 --> 00:18:33.360
you because a lot of you—I see what

00:18:31.039 --> 00:18:35.679
you're saying: "Well, God works in your

00:18:33.360 --> 00:18:37.280
life but he doesn't work in mine."You

00:18:35.679 --> 00:18:39.840
know why? Because that's what you

00:18:37.280 --> 00:18:42.639
believe. Out of the abundance of the

00:18:39.840 --> 00:18:44.720
heart, the mouth speaks. The Bible says that

00:18:42.640 --> 00:18:46.320
what you believe in your heart,

00:18:44.720 --> 00:18:48.640
you're going to say out of your mouth. You

00:18:46.320 --> 00:18:50.399
can always pinpoint somebody and where

00:18:48.640 --> 00:18:53.200
they are in their faith because of what

00:18:50.400 --> 00:18:55.360
they're saying out of their mouth. I can

00:18:53.200 --> 00:18:56.960
just get around you for five minutes

00:18:55.360 --> 00:18:58.479
to have a conversation and ask

00:18:56.960 --> 00:19:00.160
you certain questions about

00:18:58.480 --> 00:19:02.000
your life. What do you say about your

00:19:00.160 --> 00:19:04.240
life? What are you saying

00:19:02.000 --> 00:19:06.960
about your circumstances? Because I

00:19:04.240 --> 00:19:10.000
can pinpoint your faith real quick.

00:19:06.960 --> 00:19:13.440
You will never hear me speak bad about

00:19:10.000 --> 00:19:15.679
my kids, ever. I tell you examples of

00:19:13.440 --> 00:19:18.559
things to help you, but I'm telling you,

00:19:15.679 --> 00:19:20.400
I never even would let

00:19:18.559 --> 00:19:22.639
anybody speak the word "autism"out of

00:19:20.400 --> 00:19:24.080
their mouth. If you spoke "autism"over my

00:19:22.640 --> 00:19:26.000
daughter, I would want to punch you in

00:19:24.080 --> 00:19:27.918
the face. That's how much it upset

00:19:26.000 --> 00:19:30.720
me. I'd be like, "No, you ain't

00:19:27.919 --> 00:19:33.840
speaking that trash over my child. She's

00:19:30.720 --> 00:19:37.120
healed by the stripes of

00:19:33.840 --> 00:19:38.799
Jesus."It's

00:19:37.120 --> 00:19:40.719
an illustration I'm trying to tell

00:19:38.799 --> 00:19:42.000
you. Sometimes I tell you, "This is what

00:19:40.720 --> 00:19:43.840
we're overcoming,"but we don't speak

00:19:42.000 --> 00:19:46.080
that word in our house.

00:19:43.840 --> 00:19:48.000
It's like speaking death.

00:19:46.080 --> 00:19:50.639
That's a death word. We're not speaking

00:19:48.000 --> 00:19:53.039
that; we speak life. Megan is healed by

00:19:50.640 --> 00:19:55.520
the stripes of Jesus. Megan has the mind

00:19:53.039 --> 00:19:58.080
of Christ. Megan can do all things

00:19:55.520 --> 00:20:00.720
through Christ who's in her. I'm

00:19:58.080 --> 00:20:03.199
not moved by what I see. I'm not moved

00:20:00.720 --> 00:20:05.200
by what I feel right now. Yeah, she may

00:20:03.200 --> 00:20:07.200
have had a temper tantrum and she may be

00:20:05.200 --> 00:20:09.280
flipping out and doing her thing and

00:20:07.200 --> 00:20:11.120
stemming and doing all this stuff, but

00:20:09.280 --> 00:20:14.480
God, I thank you, Lord, that those

00:20:11.120 --> 00:20:16.959
things are subject to change. I am

00:20:14.480 --> 00:20:18.799
not moved by what she's doing right now

00:20:16.960 --> 00:20:21.120
when she's having an anger fit or doing

00:20:18.799 --> 00:20:23.039
something. I just pray over her mind:

00:20:21.120 --> 00:20:24.879
"Father, I lay hands on her. I bind

00:20:23.039 --> 00:20:27.200
any kind of demonic disturbances off of

00:20:24.880 --> 00:20:29.600
you, baby. You are healed in the name of

00:20:27.200 --> 00:20:31.520
Jesus. I speak to your brain cells to

00:20:29.600 --> 00:20:33.199
line up with the word of God. I speak to

00:20:31.520 --> 00:20:35.360
any damage in your body that's been

00:20:33.200 --> 00:20:38.240
caused by vaccinations to be healed in Jesus'name."You

00:20:35.360 --> 00:20:40.799
are a creative, miracle-working

00:20:38.240 --> 00:20:43.360
God, and I believe with all my

00:20:40.799 --> 00:20:46.320
heart that You raised Christ from the

00:20:43.360 --> 00:20:48.559
dead and You healed

00:20:46.320 --> 00:20:51.840
me by His stripes.

00:20:48.559 --> 00:20:55.280
I stand on that. I'm not moved by what I

00:20:51.840 --> 00:20:58.399
see. I'm not moved by what I feel; I'm

00:20:55.280 --> 00:21:01.360
moved by what the word says. God is a

00:20:58.400 --> 00:21:04.480
good God. Remember this, regardless

00:21:01.360 --> 00:21:07.918
of what your circumstances are saying

00:21:04.480 --> 00:21:11.360
around you: No. Regardless of how bad it

00:21:07.919 --> 00:21:13.440
may look—you may have the worst

00:21:11.360 --> 00:21:16.158
conditions and it doesn't look like it's changed—but

00:21:13.440 --> 00:21:18.080
if you keep on keeping on,

00:21:16.159 --> 00:21:21.200
if you keep speaking and you keep

00:21:18.080 --> 00:21:22.879
declaring and you keep looking at

00:21:21.200 --> 00:21:26.159
your circumstances, it's

00:21:22.880 --> 00:21:29.120
going to change. It takes time sometimes to

00:21:26.159 --> 00:21:31.919
move a big ship and to turn a huge

00:21:29.120 --> 00:21:35.039
ocean liner. It takes a little bit to

00:21:31.919 --> 00:21:36.640
turn that ship. Sometimes it takes a

00:21:35.039 --> 00:21:38.960
little bit because you've been speaking

00:21:36.640 --> 00:21:41.520
so much trash out of your mouth for so

00:21:38.960 --> 00:21:44.480
long. It may take a little bit, but

00:21:41.520 --> 00:21:46.240
don't give up. Don't give in to it.

00:21:44.480 --> 00:21:47.840
The devil might come by and whisper in

00:21:46.240 --> 00:21:49.360
your ear, telling you your

00:21:47.840 --> 00:21:51.439
life's never going to change, you're

00:21:49.360 --> 00:21:54.000
going to be this way forever, and there's no

00:21:51.440 --> 00:21:56.640
God that hears your prayers. But I'm

00:21:54.000 --> 00:21:58.720
telling you this, God is faithful and

00:21:56.640 --> 00:22:01.039
He's going to set you free with the same

00:21:58.720 --> 00:22:04.159
power that He set me free with.

00:22:01.039 --> 00:22:07.440
He loves you. Don't get weary in well-doing.

00:22:04.159 --> 00:22:09.600
Keep your faith stirred

00:22:07.440 --> 00:22:11.760
up. You've got to get in the word every

00:22:09.600 --> 00:22:14.399
day. You've got to get in prayer every

00:22:11.760 --> 00:22:17.200
day because you have to keep filling

00:22:14.400 --> 00:22:19.919
your spirit up with that word.

00:22:17.200 --> 00:22:22.240
Find the scripture. I've said

00:22:19.919 --> 00:22:24.080
it before and I'll say it again: you've got

00:22:22.240 --> 00:22:26.000
to find scriptures pertaining to what

00:22:24.080 --> 00:22:28.240
you're believing for. You've got to get

00:22:26.000 --> 00:22:30.559
that word down inside of your heart

00:22:28.240 --> 00:22:32.480
because in those words, that's what

00:22:30.559 --> 00:22:34.639
brings freedom. You shall know the

00:22:32.480 --> 00:22:35.840
truth, and the truth will set you free.

00:22:34.640 --> 00:22:37.840
But I'm telling you, if you keep

00:22:35.840 --> 00:22:39.678
speaking trash out of your mouth, you're

00:22:37.840 --> 00:22:41.678
going to live it. I've

00:22:39.679 --> 00:22:43.919
lived it; I saw it happen

00:22:41.679 --> 00:22:45.360
when I was growing up. A lot of times my

00:22:43.919 --> 00:22:47.200
mom would speak things out of

00:22:45.360 --> 00:22:48.959
her mouth that she didn't believe in her

00:22:47.200 --> 00:22:50.080
heart because whatever was at the abundance

00:22:48.960 --> 00:22:51.679
of the heart, the mouth speaks, what I

00:22:50.080 --> 00:22:52.879
tell you. And we

00:22:52.880 --> 00:22:55.600
kept going around the mountain. But I'm

00:22:54.080 --> 00:22:57.520
telling you, my mother started speaking

00:22:55.600 --> 00:22:59.439
better out of her mouth. She lives it

00:22:57.520 --> 00:23:00.799
now. She started speaking positive out

00:22:59.440 --> 00:23:03.520
of her mouth. She started saying things

00:23:00.799 --> 00:23:05.440
over us: "It's going to get better."And

00:23:03.520 --> 00:23:07.280
I'm telling you, after the third kid,

00:23:05.440 --> 00:23:09.200
my little brother, he had it a lot

00:23:07.280 --> 00:23:11.200
better than what I had it. When I first

00:23:09.200 --> 00:23:12.480
started out, we had it real rough. But

00:23:11.200 --> 00:23:14.000
when she started getting the word of

00:23:12.480 --> 00:23:15.760
faith and all that word down inside of

00:23:14.000 --> 00:23:16.799
her, it started changing. My little

00:23:15.760 --> 00:23:18.720
brother has a totally different life

00:23:16.799 --> 00:23:22.080
than what I had. But I'm telling you

00:23:18.720 --> 00:23:25.120
this, you can change your circumstances

00:23:22.080 --> 00:23:27.199
by your words. You need to understand

00:23:25.120 --> 00:23:30.559
how powerful your words are. And I hope

00:23:27.200 --> 00:23:32.240
I haven't become boring, but I'm just

00:23:30.559 --> 00:23:34.480
trying to tell you what's changed my

00:23:32.240 --> 00:23:36.640
life. That's what I

00:23:34.480 --> 00:23:38.640
kept saying about the mower. God

00:23:36.640 --> 00:23:40.480
is a good God. He's going to take care

00:23:38.640 --> 00:23:42.000
of me. Even whenever it didn't look like

00:23:40.480 --> 00:23:44.000
it was going to and the summer is

00:23:42.000 --> 00:23:45.840
almost over, but right when it's

00:23:44.000 --> 00:23:48.159
almost time to start doing the leaves,

00:23:45.840 --> 00:23:51.439
God says, "Brennan, I got your back. I

00:23:48.159 --> 00:23:54.320
got you."Maybe He was talking to

00:23:51.440 --> 00:23:57.039
that sister in the church for

00:23:54.320 --> 00:23:59.280
weeks ahead and she was

00:23:57.039 --> 00:24:01.840
resisting it. A lot of times, this is

00:23:59.280 --> 00:24:04.720
what I want to tell you: when God speaks

00:24:01.840 --> 00:24:07.760
to you to be obedient and to do

00:24:04.720 --> 00:24:09.840
something, do it immediately. Because if

00:24:07.760 --> 00:24:11.360
you don't, He'll bring that

00:24:09.840 --> 00:24:13.039
person who you're believing for

00:24:11.360 --> 00:24:14.799
and you're sowing those seeds. It may

00:24:13.039 --> 00:24:17.200
take you a long time. This might be

00:24:14.799 --> 00:24:18.320
something that I'm reaping. He might be

00:24:17.200 --> 00:24:20.159
telling you, 'You need to do this,

00:24:18.320 --> 00:24:21.760
this, and this.'He'll

00:24:20.159 --> 00:24:23.840
bring that same kind of

00:24:21.760 --> 00:24:26.240
person around you who was in

00:24:23.840 --> 00:24:28.240
rebellion. Basically, if he

00:24:26.240 --> 00:24:30.159
told them a long time ago, 'I wanted

00:24:28.240 --> 00:24:33.520
to give that mower to them

00:24:30.159 --> 00:24:36.559
back in June or May when the season

00:24:33.520 --> 00:24:39.039
first started,'and they resisted it—'Oh,

00:24:36.559 --> 00:24:40.559
I don't feel like it.

00:24:39.039 --> 00:24:42.400
I don't want to do that. I just

00:24:40.559 --> 00:24:43.600
paid $7,000 for that'—and they wrestle

00:24:42.400 --> 00:24:46.480
with it,

00:24:43.600 --> 00:24:48.959
the Lord keeps putting it on their heart: 'I

00:24:46.480 --> 00:24:52.720
want you to do this for Brandon.''I don't

00:24:48.960 --> 00:24:56.000
feel like doing that right now, Lord.'Don't sow

00:24:52.720 --> 00:24:57.919
those kind of seeds. When God

00:24:56.000 --> 00:25:00.480
speaks to you to do something,

00:24:57.919 --> 00:25:02.320
be quick to obey because that's

00:25:00.480 --> 00:25:04.000
the kind of seed you'll reap back. When

00:25:02.320 --> 00:25:06.639
God speaks to somebody's heart to help

00:25:04.000 --> 00:25:08.159
you out, be quick to obey.

00:25:08.159 --> 00:25:11.520
He'll start

00:25:09.760 --> 00:25:15.360
speaking to someone's heart to sow

00:25:11.520 --> 00:25:17.279
fast to

00:25:15.360 --> 00:25:18.959
you. You could be waiting on your

00:25:17.279 --> 00:25:21.520
miracle sometimes and ask, 'Where is it, Lord?'like in

00:25:18.960 --> 00:25:23.360
my situation. But there've

00:25:21.520 --> 00:25:25.520
been times he's told

00:25:23.360 --> 00:25:27.039
me, 'I want you to give a watch away.'I

00:25:25.520 --> 00:25:28.879
don't want to give that watch

00:25:27.039 --> 00:25:30.960
away because I love watches. Watches are a

00:25:28.880 --> 00:25:33.200
big deal to me. I've given seven watches

00:25:30.960 --> 00:25:34.880
away, and the Lord tells

00:25:33.200 --> 00:25:37.360
me it's like a ministry to me. I

00:25:34.880 --> 00:25:38.799
love watches. So I give these

00:25:37.360 --> 00:25:40.000
watches away, and the Lord said,

00:25:38.799 --> 00:25:41.840
'See that person over there in

00:25:40.000 --> 00:25:43.919
church? I want you to.'My first watch I

00:25:41.840 --> 00:25:46.480
ever gave away, I was 15 years old and I

00:25:43.919 --> 00:25:48.159
paid $400 for it; it was a Seiko.

00:25:46.480 --> 00:25:49.600
It was really dear to me because it was

00:25:48.159 --> 00:25:50.799
one of those kinetic ones

00:25:49.600 --> 00:25:53.120
that you could move your arm and

00:25:50.799 --> 00:25:55.279
it would charge itself.

00:25:53.120 --> 00:25:57.840
And the Lord spoke to me, 'I want you to

00:25:55.279 --> 00:26:01.120
give that watch to the youth pastor.'It

00:25:57.840 --> 00:26:02.559
was really nice back then; for me,

00:26:01.120 --> 00:26:06.080
that was a lot of money. It took me

00:26:02.559 --> 00:26:08.320
forever to save up for that watch.

00:26:06.080 --> 00:26:10.399
I kept resisting it and was like,

00:26:08.320 --> 00:26:12.320
'Please Lord, I don't want to give

00:26:10.400 --> 00:26:14.159
that watch away.'It took me

00:26:12.320 --> 00:26:15.600
months to save for that watch because I

00:26:14.159 --> 00:26:17.600
was sacking groceries,

00:26:15.600 --> 00:26:19.199
just

00:26:17.600 --> 00:26:21.520
putting groceries up, and I only

00:26:19.200 --> 00:26:23.600
made minimum wage. Back then,

00:26:21.520 --> 00:26:25.360
that was nothing. I kept

00:26:23.600 --> 00:26:26.959
resisting it and I didn't

00:26:25.360 --> 00:26:28.240
want to sow, but I had to do my tithes and

00:26:26.960 --> 00:26:31.039
offerings and everything. The Lord said, 'I

00:26:28.240 --> 00:26:33.200
want you to give that watch to him.'One

00:26:31.039 --> 00:26:34.799
day I was at church

00:26:33.200 --> 00:26:36.400
and he walked by me, and the Lord said,

00:26:34.799 --> 00:26:38.320
'Give that watch to him right now. I want

00:26:36.400 --> 00:26:40.640
you to be

00:26:38.320 --> 00:26:42.559
obedient to what I told you to do.'So I

00:26:40.640 --> 00:26:44.720
took my watch off and I said, 'Hey,

00:26:42.559 --> 00:26:46.799
pastor. The Lord spoke to me

00:26:44.720 --> 00:26:48.640
to give this watch to you.

00:26:46.799 --> 00:26:51.120
This is a sacrificial gift, and

00:26:48.640 --> 00:26:53.600
it's painful for my

00:26:51.120 --> 00:26:55.600
flesh because it took me over three

00:26:53.600 --> 00:26:58.158
months to save up for this. 400 bucks.'So

00:26:55.600 --> 00:26:59.439
I

00:26:58.159 --> 00:27:02.480
gave it to him and I prayed over him. I

00:26:59.440 --> 00:27:04.799
cried as I did it.

00:27:02.480 --> 00:27:06.799
But I'm trying to tell you, God

00:27:04.799 --> 00:27:08.320
is faithful and he always provides

00:27:06.799 --> 00:27:09.918
another watch. He always takes care of

00:27:08.320 --> 00:27:11.120
things. I started sowing those watches, and the

00:27:09.919 --> 00:27:13.360
Lord gives me better watches.

00:27:11.120 --> 00:27:15.120
So this is a thing for

00:27:13.360 --> 00:27:17.678
me.

00:27:15.120 --> 00:27:19.678
I'm wanting you to understand

00:27:17.679 --> 00:27:21.120
that sometimes God will speak to your

00:27:19.679 --> 00:27:22.799
heart and tell you to do something

00:27:21.120 --> 00:27:24.639
that's not always comfortable to your

00:27:22.799 --> 00:27:26.400
flesh. It wasn't

00:27:24.640 --> 00:27:29.120
comfortable to the lady that gave me the

00:27:26.400 --> 00:27:31.360
$7,000 mower

00:27:29.120 --> 00:27:33.120
she just bought

00:27:31.360 --> 00:27:36.000
over a year ago. It was

00:27:33.120 --> 00:27:38.158
almost brand new.

00:27:36.000 --> 00:27:40.000
It's not comfortable sometimes.

00:27:38.159 --> 00:27:42.080
It makes you

00:27:40.000 --> 00:27:44.240
want to go 'ooh,'but

00:27:42.080 --> 00:27:46.480
there's reward

00:27:44.240 --> 00:27:48.720
in it. There've been so many times

00:27:46.480 --> 00:27:50.159
that I sow and it's painful.

00:27:50.159 --> 00:27:54.799
But

00:27:51.600 --> 00:27:56.480
you have to move in faith for your

00:27:54.799 --> 00:27:59.520
circumstances. You've got

00:27:56.480 --> 00:28:01.919
to put your faith into motion and

00:27:59.520 --> 00:28:04.158
do things that

00:28:01.919 --> 00:28:06.399
are uncomfortable.

00:28:04.159 --> 00:28:08.240
God is a faithful God. And if you sow

00:28:06.399 --> 00:28:09.760
into good ground and you sow and you

00:28:08.240 --> 00:28:11.679
do these things, God will always come

00:28:09.760 --> 00:28:13.679
through for you. I'm just trying to tell

00:28:11.679 --> 00:28:15.440
you what I've lived, y'all.

00:28:15.440 --> 00:28:20.480
I do it all the time.

00:28:17.760 --> 00:28:22.399
And God is a faithful God. So if the

00:28:20.480 --> 00:28:24.000
Lord tells you to bless your church or the

00:28:22.399 --> 00:28:26.000
lady at

00:28:24.000 --> 00:28:28.640
the grocery store and you don't want to

00:28:26.000 --> 00:28:30.960
help, she might be down to

00:28:28.640 --> 00:28:32.640
her last $50.

00:28:33.679 --> 00:28:37.679
You could

00:28:36.000 --> 00:28:40.240
be the greatest influence and the

00:28:37.679 --> 00:28:42.320
greatest blessing to that person at that

00:28:40.240 --> 00:28:44.399
moment and

00:28:42.320 --> 00:28:45.520
just tell them, 'Jesus loves you and I

00:28:44.399 --> 00:28:48.158
just want to pray for you.'They may

00:28:45.520 --> 00:28:49.440
go, 'I need prayer.'Kind of

00:28:48.159 --> 00:28:51.760
like when I prayed for the man that had

00:28:49.440 --> 00:28:53.919
the bad lung problem. He was

00:28:51.760 --> 00:28:55.360
desperate and needed his

00:28:53.919 --> 00:28:57.440
miracle right then, or he

00:28:55.360 --> 00:28:59.120
was getting ready to die. What an

00:28:57.440 --> 00:29:01.039
opportunity to be a blessing!

00:28:59.120 --> 00:29:02.559
I

00:29:01.039 --> 00:29:04.000
see the comment section, and I'm just

00:29:02.559 --> 00:29:06.080
trying to go by what I see.

00:29:04.000 --> 00:29:07.679
A

00:29:06.080 --> 00:29:09.279
lady's talking about how she's broke and

00:29:07.679 --> 00:29:10.640
can't pay for her food.

00:29:09.279 --> 00:29:12.720
I'm telling you how

00:29:10.640 --> 00:29:14.640
God's always provided for me. I

00:29:12.720 --> 00:29:16.799
wanted to tell you a testimony about

00:29:14.640 --> 00:29:19.840
what God did for me this evening just

00:29:16.799 --> 00:29:21.200
yesterday. God's so faithful and God

00:29:19.840 --> 00:29:23.520
will take care of you if you believe

00:29:21.200 --> 00:29:25.120
him. But you have to start speaking and

00:29:23.520 --> 00:29:26.799
believing

00:29:25.120 --> 00:29:28.320
better. When you

00:29:26.799 --> 00:29:29.918
do,

00:29:28.320 --> 00:29:31.360
God's going to turn

00:29:29.919 --> 00:29:32.320
your mountain around. He's

00:29:31.360 --> 00:29:33.600
a

00:29:32.320 --> 00:29:35.360
mountain-dissolving

00:29:33.600 --> 00:29:38.639
God.

00:29:38.640 --> 00:29:45.520
We are in

00:29:42.000 --> 00:29:47.200
the greatest days for the

00:29:45.520 --> 00:29:50.320
body of Christ to be a light and

00:29:47.200 --> 00:29:54.799
to be the salt. It's a choice. But

00:29:50.320 --> 00:29:56.879
Jesus needs us to

00:29:54.799 --> 00:29:58.080
be obedient. If we're not,

00:29:56.880 --> 00:29:59.760
we're not doing what he's called us to

00:29:58.080 --> 00:30:02.559
do.

00:30:03.919 --> 00:30:07.279
He's ready to come back, but

00:30:05.919 --> 00:30:09.120
he's wanting those souls coming in.

00:30:07.279 --> 00:30:10.799
If you have something on

00:30:09.120 --> 00:30:13.520
your heart and you need direction,

00:30:10.799 --> 00:30:15.120
or for

00:30:13.520 --> 00:30:16.399
preaching like

00:30:15.120 --> 00:30:18.000
these little sermons I'm doing,

00:30:16.399 --> 00:30:19.439
tell me, 'Hey, I'm

00:30:18.000 --> 00:30:21.200
believing for

00:30:19.440 --> 00:30:22.559
this.'I'm

00:30:21.200 --> 00:30:24.559
trying to

00:30:22.559 --> 00:30:26.399
give you encouragement by telling you

00:30:24.559 --> 00:30:28.000
how my wife and I have lived

00:30:26.399 --> 00:30:30.719
this. We're not

00:30:28.000 --> 00:30:34.240
perfect. One time we

00:30:30.720 --> 00:30:36.559
had our maternity and the

00:30:34.240 --> 00:30:39.840
doctor's bills were thousands of

00:30:36.559 --> 00:30:41.039
dollars. We were

00:30:39.840 --> 00:30:42.639
broke.

00:30:41.039 --> 00:30:46.240
I was working at the church and we

00:30:42.640 --> 00:30:48.880
were real desperate. The

00:30:46.240 --> 00:30:51.120
hospital sent the bill to a

00:30:48.880 --> 00:30:52.559
collection agency,

00:30:51.120 --> 00:30:54.799
and they were going

00:30:52.559 --> 00:30:57.200
to garnish our wages.

00:30:54.799 --> 00:31:00.080
It's the way it is here in Oklahoma.

00:30:57.200 --> 00:31:01.600
If you don't pay

00:31:00.080 --> 00:31:03.120
your bills,

00:31:01.600 --> 00:31:04.719
they're able to come after

00:31:03.120 --> 00:31:06.959
you.

00:31:04.720 --> 00:31:08.960
Rightfully so, I owed the money, but

00:31:06.960 --> 00:31:11.200
I just didn't have it.

00:31:13.039 --> 00:31:15.440
We were living on food stamps. They were

00:31:14.240 --> 00:31:17.360
saying, 'We're going to garnish your checks.'We

00:31:15.440 --> 00:31:19.200
were like, 'God, what

00:31:17.360 --> 00:31:23.360
are we going to do?'We couldn't even pay

00:31:19.200 --> 00:31:26.080
our rent. So we were just

00:31:23.360 --> 00:31:28.240
standing by faith. And this is

00:31:26.080 --> 00:31:29.678
another circumstance.

00:31:28.240 --> 00:31:31.679
This was something that was really

00:31:29.679 --> 00:31:34.240
dear to me at the time because God came

00:31:31.679 --> 00:31:35.440
through.

00:31:34.240 --> 00:31:36.480
I was

00:31:35.440 --> 00:31:38.000
cleaning the bathrooms of the church. I was

00:31:36.480 --> 00:31:39.440
keeping my head up and I said, "God,

00:31:38.000 --> 00:31:40.799
they're coming after my check,

00:31:39.440 --> 00:31:42.720
they're going to take part

00:31:40.799 --> 00:31:44.480
of it, and I don't have it. We're going

00:31:42.720 --> 00:31:46.240
to go without food again."I

00:31:44.480 --> 00:31:49.279
was just whining inside my

00:31:46.240 --> 00:31:52.960
heart, trying to keep my faith up.

00:31:49.279 --> 00:31:55.039
Some people in the church...

00:31:52.960 --> 00:31:56.799
we didn't tell anybody anything because

00:31:55.039 --> 00:32:00.000
I'm not a person who

00:31:56.799 --> 00:32:03.440
manipulates. Don't be a person who is

00:32:00.000 --> 00:32:06.559
manipulating people by the ministry of

00:32:03.440 --> 00:32:09.039
hints. Don't do that.

00:32:06.559 --> 00:32:10.720
God is your provider. Man is not. You

00:32:09.039 --> 00:32:12.320
need to understand that. Don't go around

00:32:10.720 --> 00:32:14.480
telling people at church, "Well, I'm

00:32:12.320 --> 00:32:16.879
having a hard time and I can't pay my bills."Tell

00:32:14.480 --> 00:32:20.399
God and

00:32:16.880 --> 00:32:22.960
rejoice. Keep your eyes on Jesus. Don't

00:32:20.399 --> 00:32:24.158
put your eyes on man. My wife, Diana,

00:32:22.960 --> 00:32:26.320
was working. We were doing the best

00:32:24.159 --> 00:32:28.240
we could. I was in there cleaning and

00:32:26.320 --> 00:32:30.639
I got a call on my radio: "Hey, come to

00:32:28.240 --> 00:32:34.000
the front."I

00:32:30.640 --> 00:32:35.519
went up to the front and there was

00:32:34.000 --> 00:32:38.080
a lady there. She said, "The

00:32:35.519 --> 00:32:42.600
Lord told me to write you a check to pay

00:32:38.080 --> 00:32:42.600
off your hospital

00:32:43.039 --> 00:32:50.480
bills."It

00:32:47.519 --> 00:32:53.840
took my breath away because I

00:32:50.480 --> 00:32:56.720
was so desperate.

00:32:53.840 --> 00:32:58.720
I called my

00:32:56.720 --> 00:33:00.559
wife and said, "Hey, babe, look

00:32:58.720 --> 00:33:02.559
what Jesus just did."She gave me a

00:33:00.559 --> 00:33:04.080
check for $3,500.

00:33:02.559 --> 00:33:06.399
She said, "The Lord told me to give you

00:33:04.080 --> 00:33:08.000
this

00:33:06.399 --> 00:33:10.879
to pay off your

00:33:08.000 --> 00:33:14.159
hospital bills, what you still owed."And

00:33:10.880 --> 00:33:16.640
God took care of all of it.

00:33:14.159 --> 00:33:18.960
We were right there at the

00:33:16.640 --> 00:33:21.519
point of them garnishing my wages. But

00:33:18.960 --> 00:33:24.559
I'm trying to tell you, God is a

00:33:21.519 --> 00:33:26.960
faithful God. And if you believe him,

00:33:24.559 --> 00:33:28.799
nothing is impossible to him who

00:33:26.960 --> 00:33:29.760
believes. So let me pray for you right

00:33:28.799 --> 00:33:31.279
now.

00:33:29.760 --> 00:33:33.279
Will you bow your heads? I'm going

00:33:31.279 --> 00:33:34.720
to believe God. You may need a financial

00:33:33.279 --> 00:33:36.080
miracle or

00:33:34.720 --> 00:33:37.919
breakthrough. You may need healing in

00:33:36.080 --> 00:33:39.678
your body.

00:33:37.919 --> 00:33:41.279
I don't know what circumstances you

00:33:39.679 --> 00:33:43.840
are in, but I know it doesn't

00:33:41.279 --> 00:33:46.960
matter what it is. All things are

00:33:43.840 --> 00:33:49.519
possible. Nothing is too

00:33:46.960 --> 00:33:50.960
big. So, Father, right now, just stretch

00:33:49.519 --> 00:33:52.559
your hands out to me. I'm going to

00:33:50.960 --> 00:33:54.880
believe God with you right now.

00:33:52.559 --> 00:33:56.320
Wherever you are, you might be all

00:33:54.880 --> 00:33:58.320
around the world. You may be down to your

00:33:56.320 --> 00:34:00.399
last cup of rice. There are some people

00:33:58.320 --> 00:34:03.279
all over the place that I'm

00:34:00.399 --> 00:34:05.600
ministering to right now. You may be to

00:34:03.279 --> 00:34:07.919
your last cup of beans. Who knows? But I

00:34:05.600 --> 00:34:10.560
know this: God's a multiplier. God's a

00:34:07.919 --> 00:34:13.679
God that provides. So, Father, right now

00:34:10.560 --> 00:34:15.199
in the name of Jesus, I speak to their

00:34:13.679 --> 00:34:17.040
circumstances.

00:34:15.199 --> 00:34:20.000
I agree with my brothers and sisters

00:34:17.040 --> 00:34:22.800
right now. We speak

00:34:20.000 --> 00:34:25.839
life out of our mouths concerning our

